“30th Century Twin Killer” was created by @sayfbahr in 2021
 In the 21st century, there was a tragic incident of tortures and killing act of animals by mankind.  Only rabbits managed to escape the tragic incident. In this 30th century, the ancestors of rabbits have given birth to new generations to avenge the events that happened in the 21st century. A pair of twin rabbits have succeeded in massacring humanity, they celebrate by eating human flesh as a form of respect for the victory of revenge.
